---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="velvetgrl privacy policy.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-stone">
      <p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

      <h2>Responsible Party</h2>
      <p>
        Jonas August Menesklou<br />
        Finkenweg 10<br />
        76761 R&uuml;lzheim, Germany<br />
        E-Mail: <a href="mailto:jonas.menesklou@gmail.com">jonas.menesklou@gmail.com</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Data Collection on This Website</h2>
      <p>When you visit velvetgrl.com, we collect anonymous usage data through Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. This includes pages visited, time on site, referral source, and general geographic region. No personally identifiable information is collected unless you voluntarily provide it (e.g., by contacting us via email).</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>This website uses cookies. When you first visit, a cookie banner asks for your consent. Only if you accept will analytics cookies be set. You can revoke your consent at any time by clearing your browser cookies.</p>
      <p>We use the following types of cookies:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Cookie consent preference (always active)</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Google Analytics (only with your consent) &mdash; to understand site usage and improve our content</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Google Analytics</h2>
      <p>This website uses Google Analytics, a web analytics service provided by Google LLC. Google Analytics uses cookies to analyze your use of the website. The information generated by the cookie about your use of this website is usually transferred to a Google server in the USA and stored there. We have activated IP anonymization, so your IP address is shortened by Google within the EU before transmission.</p>
      <p>You can prevent the collection of data by Google Analytics by declining cookies via our cookie banner, or by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>Our pages may contain links to external websites. We have no influence over the content and data protection practices of external sites. Please refer to the privacy policies of the respective providers.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under the GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request information about your stored personal data</li>
        <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Restrict or object to data processing</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or your data, contact us at <a href="mailto:jonas.menesklou@gmail.com">jonas.menesklou@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
